name: The Mellow Colour Co. #383
description: The second Mint in The Mellow Colour Co. This OBJKT was minted cycle 383. All remaining editions will be burned cycle 385. This piece is originally priced at the equivalent of 1 USD. A new piece will be released every cycle with all remaining editions burned 2 cycles later. Collect the second piece in TMCC. (TMCC #377 was minted corresponding to the rewards cycle. For now on OBJKT’s will be minted and numbered during Baking Cycles instead. Remaining editions of #377 will be burned cycle #384)
